He didn't enter a plea today.

09:22.395 --> 09:26.032 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Rahimi was born in Afghanistan,
but is now
a U.S. citizen.

09:26.065 --> 09:30.603 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: And the man
who bills himself
America's toughest sheriff has
been turned

09:30.637 --> 09:32.405 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
out of office.

09:32.439 --> 09:37.510 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Longtime Arizona lawman Joe
Arpaio lost his
