24 years in

09:37.544 --> 09:39.012 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
office.

09:39.045 --> 09:41.581 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
He'd gained prominence for his
aggressive
stance on illegal immigration.

09:41.614 --> 09:46.286 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But he also sparked federal
investigations
of alleged racial profiling.

09:46.319 --> 09:52.525 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Still to come on the "NewsHour":
what a President
Trump could do in his first 100
days in office;

09:52.559 --> 09:58.598 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
why women didn't vote the way
