09:58.631 --> 10:04.337 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Iraqi city; and much more.

10:04.370 --> 10:16.583 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: A peaceful
