Obama and the
people around him?

15:57.056 --> 16:00.159 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
And, conversely, what is
President Obama looking
for from the Trump team?

16:00.193 --> 16:06.365 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NANCY GIBBS: Well, you know,
this is going
to be so interesting to watch,
because, naturally,

16:06.399 --> 16:11.103 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
anyone who has just been elected
president
