19:04.110 --> 19:07.580 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SCOTT HORSLEY, National Public
Radio: Well,
some of the things, like
repealing Obamacare,

19:07.613 --> 19:09.148 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
