day three.

19:16.522 --> 19:18.290 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Day one, I think, is a Saturday.

19:18.324 --> 19:23.029 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But very early on, he can start
to undo some
of the executive orders that
President Obama

19:23.062 --> 19:24.864 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
has put in place.

19:24.897 --> 19:29.502 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And President Obama has used
executive orders
